{"tid":1285141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「局勢」香港人已經沒有退路","createTime":"2019-07-04T12:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T12:49:46.000Z","uid":116134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"057156938341a318c81637f39402ef2448ba4d14","tid":1285141,"uid":116134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"香港人已經沒有退路，今次反送中運動已經向北京充分展示咗香港人真正嘅本質同意願，一百萬人、612、二百萬人、解放立法會，呢啲都係香港人對一國兩制同中共不信任嘅證據。今後，北京將會前所未有咁加大力度打壓香港民主。所以一日唔達到目的都唔可以收手。只有贏勝仗，敵人先會心生敬畏。我地已經無路可退，回頭只會係五年前嘅舊路。"},{"pid":"e30bf60a28b34c5fa5971d4c490f6fcf021ab2b1","tid":1285141,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4f8184271a1744bed3136aa92a6ab01fb7ce663","tid":1285141,"uid":117399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"736de1355a69414ce10218352a97ab1e35dfdedd","tid":1285141,"uid":227301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"我無野講"}]}